txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Tough branches from the twisted creatures of nature in Haragmar and Agamaur. Bring them to Elsa the Bold at the Eglain-camp at Agamaur.
'This is a painful effort, but one that must be done.\n\n'Thank you.'
'Radagast says that much of the nature will return, but some is too far gone. Can you purge the creatures of nature to the south and west and bring proof that they suffer no longer?'
Elsa the Bold, at the Eglain-camp in Agamaur, desires tough branches from the twisted creatures of nature found in Haragmar and Agamaur.
Deliver the tough branchess to Elsa the Bold at the Eglain-camp at Agamaur
You accepted a task, for Elsa the Bold, to acquire tough branches from the creatures of nature within the swamp of Agamaur. You can find Elsa the Bold within the Eglain-camp at Agamaur.
Wanted: Tough branches from the twisted creatures of nature in Haragmar and Agamaur.
